Subject: Re: [T2] Bolt for Sliding Door Handle

All VW shows is a standard flat washer in the diagram.

N011 524 23

The size shown is different from most standard 6mm flat washers: 6.4
(1/4") ID x12.5 (1/2") OD x1.6mm Thick, almost like what we in the USA
call a "body washer".

